726287f-a.text:
Brookville Park (Queens): Viewing southwestward across Conselyea's Pond from near Brookville Boulevard and Edgewood Avenue.

View 2 is northeastward from the same vantage point and shows an old pumping station of the City's department of
water supply.

P. L. Sperr  Views 1,2: March 9, 1927
